attributes.Long form description: The student begins to assemble the table, first assembles the two table legs and then screws the hex sockets on each leg with the Allen wrench. Once the screws are in place, the student has to assemble the circle on top of the table to finally place the tray and leave the table assembled.

attributes.Transcription: Now we are looking an IKEA furniture.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the white legs of the table.

attributes.Transcription: You should start by taking the two sets of legs and intertwining them together.
